unittitle_ssm: Diplomatic visits of rulers of Saudi Arabia, photograph collection
abstract_ssm: Photographic prints (27) of rulers of the Kingdom of Saudi Arabia, in primarily diplomatic visits to various countries, including the United States, United Kingdom, Spain, Morocco, Egypt, and the United Nations headquarters in New York.  Rulers depicted include King Saud and King Faisal, both after their accessions to the throne, as well as in their prior positions.
